cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper deals with image processing and machine learning techniques for vehicle type recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of SVM classifier and feature extraction techniques such as histogram and CENTROG also suggest the involvement of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of thermal images and the need to handle low resolution and lack of color information may also suggest the involvement of the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
